Rating: 3
If you get good quality ingredients I can see how this would work. You need really good prosciutto, a fresh, sweet peach, decent bread toasted just right, and honey that packs a punch. Timing is also critical. Need to serve it right away. Otherwise this could be a dull mess. Mine was somewhere between good and alright. Needed a kick. Herb? Oregano? Marjoram?

