Rating: 4
These were absolutely to die for!! Perfect combination of sweet and savory. I drizzled the bread slices with olive oil and baked rather than grilling. Next time, I would make these closer to serving -- I assembled about an hour before my guests arrived so that I could do the hot apps closer to party time and the peaches had started to bruise by the time that I served them.

